le=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">　　</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">　　抄送：省卫计委、省护理学会、市卫计委、各县（市、区）卫计委</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">　　</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">　　附件1:      “护理管理暨护理安全管理培训班”参会回执</span></p><p>　　<img src=\"http://www.ycsyy.com/upload/images/2019/11/2b264cb7fa80b425.png\" title=\"image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"/></p><p><br/></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'[db:作者]\',\n  \'editer\' => \'[db:编辑]\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2018-10-05\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2018-10-05\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'b7adb3c0be5ffc6e\',\n  \'views\' => \'[db:浏览量]\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'admin5\',\n  \'attribute\' => \n  array (\n    6 => 6,\n  ),\n)','1626157010');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` VALUES ('1137','2','admin5','添加内容','/admin.php/cms/item-add','192.168.162.110','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'933\',\n  \'title\' => \'关于《护士规范化培训》结业护理专业知识理论考试 及护理操作技能考核的通知\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'[db:来源]\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">各护理单元及相关科室：<br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">根据《护士规范化培训》计划的要求，护理部将对经过规范化培训的相关护理人员进行护理专业知识理论及护理技能操作结业考试、考核工作。具体通知如下：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">一、对象（具体名单见医院内网）：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　1、2015届护理人员；2、上年度缺考及考核不及格人员。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">二、考试内容：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　《实用临床护理“三基”——应知应会》</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　《实用临床护理“三基”——个案护理》</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　《护理工作制度手册》</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　《创建资料汇编（第九册）——护理工作流程及应急预案》</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 2em;\">三、时间及地点安排</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　理论考试：2018年9月19日15:00—16:00</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　地点：北区急诊七楼会议中心</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　操作考核：2018年9月20日14:30—17:30</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　地点：北区临床实训中心</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">注：1、时间为进医院工作时间。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　2、各护理单元安排好工作，保证相关人员准时参考。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　3、操作考核项目：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　（1）必考项目：CPR</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　（2）抽考项目：心电监护、血糖监测、钢针静脉输液。（结合案例）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　4、外出帮忙人员请相关科室负责通知到位。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">　　5、考试考核不合格者本年度不参加补考，延续至下一年补考，考试考核成绩直接与个人晋级晋升及科室绩效挂钩。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: right;\" dir=\"rtl\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">护理部</span></p><p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">018年9月11日</span> </p><p>　　</p><p><br/></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'[db:作者]\',\n  \'editer\' => \'[db:编辑]\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2018-09-11\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2018-09-11\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://